Thanks for the suggestion.... it works !  it really does....  >>>  How do I embed a video Click the embed icon under the video. It will bring up the file..right click and copy. On OFC... use the Full Editor... down on the lower left there is a "click to configure post options". Click that... and under post options turn on HTML Auto. Paste your video embed file into the post... then hit Add reply.  <<<<
